@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### ============== Operators ==============

### _gte / _lte: range filter (views between 100 and 200)
GET {{baseUrl}}/posts?views_gte=100&views_lte=200

### _ne: exclude a value (exclude post id=1)
GET {{baseUrl}}/posts?id_ne=1

### _like: RegExp filter (title contains "server")
GET {{baseUrl}}/posts?title_like=server
